した。その日、多くの人々が命を落とす――\r\n\r\n脚本：浦畑達彦 / 絵コンテ：高橋亨 / 演出：田中貴大 / 総作画監督：谷 拓也、つなきあき / 作画監督：五十川久史、鎌田均、千葉茂、中島美子、金 澤龍","status":"Air"},{"id":1050086,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1050086","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"仲間","name_cn":"同伴","duration":"00:22:50","airdate":"2021-10-27","comment":23,"desc":"2001年11月24日。総合戦闘技術評価演習を優秀な成績でクリアした白銀武たちは、いよいよ戦術機操縦訓練へと移った。\r\n\r\n初めてのシミュレータで前人未到のスコアを叩き出す武。高く評価された武たちには訓練用の戦術機が充てがわれることとなった。\r\n\r\nそして訪れた格納庫で武は、この国で唯ひとつ――将軍専用の戦術機を目撃するのだった。\r\n\r\n脚本：イシノアツオ\r\n絵コンテ：斎藤 久\r\n演出：曽根利幸\r\n総作画監督：谷 拓也　つなきあき\r\n作画監督：緒方浩美　安達祐輔　吉田和香子　山村俊了　小澤和則　清水勝祐　上西麻耶　和田伸一","status":"Air"},{"id":1050087,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1050087","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"00:22:50","airdate":"2021-11-03","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":1050088,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1050088","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"00:22:50","airdate":"2021-11-10","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":1050089,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1050089","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"00:22:50","airdate":"2021-11-17","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":1050090,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1050090","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"00:22:50","airdate":"2021-11-24","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":1050091,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1050091","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"00:22:50","airdate":"2021-12-01","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":1050092,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1050092","type":0,"sort":10,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"00:22:50","airdate":"2021-12-08","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":1050093,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1050093","type":0,"sort":11,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"00:22:50","airdate":"2021-12-15","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":1050094,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1050094","type":0,"sort":12,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"00:22:50","airdate":"2021-12-22","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"}],"crt":[{"id":16867,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/